I do.

08:40.380 --> 08:43.909
But it’s--
This thing,
I can’t explain it.

08:45.380 --> 08:46.910
What is it you’re seeing?

08:47.880 --> 08:49.850
It looks like people,

08:49.850 --> 08:51.650
but it’s--
it’s not a person.

08:52.950 --> 08:54.760
I’m not sure I understand.

08:54.760 --> 08:57.200
It looks like people.
It looks like different people.

08:57.200 --> 08:59.860
Sometimes it pretends
to be someone that I know.

08:59.860 --> 09:02.630
Sometimes it’s
a random stranger.
Sometimes--

09:02.630 --> 09:05.340
