my grandfather

09:05.340 --> 09:07.770
who died in front of me
when I was seven.

09:10.340 --> 09:12.680
But it’s all the same thing.
It--

09:14.710 --> 09:17.010
It’s-- It’s like--

09:18.910 --> 09:22.690
