01:18:48.950 --> 01:18:51.820
I can’t kill someone!

01:18:53.180 --> 01:18:54.360
You?

01:18:55.120 --> 01:18:57.280
You have it?

01:18:58.690 --> 01:19:02.470
No, no, no.
Why the fuck did you come here?

01:19:02.470 --> 01:19:04.230
You’re not giving it
back to me.

01:19:04.230 --> 01:19:06.290
Get out of here!
I’m sorry.

01:19:06.290 --> 01:19:07.600
Get out of here!

01:19:07.600 --> 01:19:16.040
Get her away from me!

01:19:23.210 --> 01:19:24.490
Hey.

01:19:25.420 --> 01:19:27.150
Hey! Wait.

01:19:29.250 --> 01:19:31.050
   What happened in there?
Nothing.

01:19:31.790 --> 01:19:33.190
What’d he say?

01:19:34.830 --> 01:19:36.060
Nothing.

01:19:36.730 --> 01:19:38.770
Nothing?

01:19:38.770 --> 01:19:40.730
He’s out of his fucking mind,
Joel.

01:21:25.230 --> 01:21:26.610
Ah, fuck.

01:22:21.490 --> 01:22:23.460
What are you doing here?

01:22:23.460 --> 01:22:25.430
I apologize
if you felt ambushed yesterday.

01:22:25.430 --> 01:22:27.160
That was the wrong approach.

01:22:27.160 --> 01:22:28.330
   I’m sorry.
Yeah.

01:22:28.330 --> 01:22:30.710
I think you should go.
               Rose.

01:22:30.710 --> 01:22:33.610
We both know
I have a responsibility
to notify the authorities

01:22:33.610 --> 01:22:36.110
if you’re a danger
to yourself or others.

01:22:36.110 --> 01:22:38.950
I need you to help convince me
you’re not a danger.

01:22:51.860 --> 01:22:54.360
Trevor mentioned
 there had been
 talk of ghosts.

01:22:55.570 --> 01:22:57.700
I never used the word
"ghosts."

01:22:59.260 --> 01:23:01.940
Evil beings, then.
Paranormal.

01:23:04.470 --> 01:23:08.810
I admitted to him
that I was seeing things,
the same thing that I told you.

01:23:08.810 --> 01:23:10.410
That’s not happening anymore.
Okay?

01:23:10.410 --> 01:23:14.150
It was stress
and lack of sleep.

01:23:14.150 --> 01:23:16.920
I confided in him, and that
was obviously a mistake.

01:23:17.380 --> 01:23:19.150
But that’s it.

01:23:19.150 --> 01:23:21.120
Okay? Are we good?

01:23:22.480 --> 01:23:24.630
How are you feeling today?

01:23:28.160 --> 01:23:29.460
Let me think, um--

01:23:30.600 --> 01:23:33.000
I’m pretty sure my fiancé
thinks I’m crazy.

01:23:34.640 --> 01:23:39.810
My sister has just
totally shut me out.

01:23:39.810 --> 01:23:41.300
And now

01:23:42.170 --> 01:23:43.750
my former therapist

01:23:43.750 --> 01:23:47.150
is making unannounced
house calls

01:23:47.150 --> 01:23:49.650
to ensure that
I am not a danger.

01:23:49.650 --> 01:23:53.320
So, other than that,
I’m really good.

01:24:03.100 --> 01:24:05.060
Should you get that?

01:24:10.230 --> 01:24:11.500
What?

01:24:11.500 --> 01:24:14.170
Rose, it’s Madeline.

01:24:14.170 --> 01:24:17.180
I’ve been trying your mobile
all morning.

01:24:17.180 --> 01:24:20.010
I’m very concerned about
how we left things yesterday.

01:24:22.310 --> 01:24:25.550
Rose? Are you there?
      No.

01:24:30.790 --> 01:24:32.120
Hello?

01:24:32.960 --> 01:24:34.670
      No.
Rose?

01:24:35.460 --> 01:24:37.460
No. No.

01:24:37.460 --> 01:24:39.670
Almost time, Rose.

01:24:41.100 --> 01:24:42.940
What the fuck are you?

01:24:46.440 --> 01:24:47.710
Ple-- Please.

01:24:51.310 --> 01:24:52.540
No, no.

01:24:53.310 --> 01:24:55.250
No. No, no.

01:25:01.290 --> 01:25:02.650
No.

01:26:12.650 --> 01:26:14.620
Hey, Dr. Cotter.

01:26:14.620 --> 01:26:17.100
Aren’t you supposed to be
on leave?

01:26:17.100 --> 01:26:19.630
Just grabbing something
from my office.

01:26:59.170 --> 01:27:01.240
Carl. Hi.

01:27:05.240 --> 01:27:06.880
                   No. No.
It’s okay.

01:27:06.880 --> 01:27:08.480
No, no, no.

01:27:08.480 --> 01:27:10.320
It’s okay.
                Oh, God.

01:27:10.320 --> 01:27:12.480
No, no. Oh, no, no, no.

01:27:12.480 --> 01:27:14.780
Shh. Shh. Just calm down.
               No! No, no!

01:27:14.780 --> 01:27:17.930
No! No!
Shh! Shut the fuck up.

01:27:19.390 --> 01:27:21.060
Just calm down, okay? Okay.

01:27:21.060 --> 01:27:22.330
Rose.

01:27:23.200 --> 01:27:24.460
What are you doing here?

01:27:27.900 --> 01:27:29.430
I don’t know.

01:27:31.300 --> 01:27:33.470
Rose, you can’t
be around patients.

01:28:06.110 --> 01:28:07.800
Fuck! Rose!

01:28:27.820 --> 01:28:30.790
Fuck!

01:28:45.610 --> 01:28:47.540
Rose, what are you
doing here?

01:28:48.220 --> 01:28:49.580
Nothing.

01:28:50.680 --> 01:28:52.350
I don’t-- I don’t know.

01:28:52.350 --> 01:28:55.390
I don’t know why. I, uh--

01:28:55.390 --> 01:28:57.720
Why don’t we go inside together
and we can just talk?

01:28:57.720 --> 01:28:59.330
No! It’s--

01:28:59.330 --> 01:29:00.890
It’s not safe.

01:29:00.890 --> 01:29:03.030
Rose, I don’t think you should
be alone right now.

01:29:03.030 --> 01:29:04.660
I need--
I need to be alone.

01:29:06.830 --> 01:29:08.940
I need to be--
I need to be alone.

01:29:11.240 --> 01:29:13.770
I’m sorry. I’m sorry.
I have to go.

01:29:15.770 --> 01:29:18.380
Rose, I don’t think you should
go anywhere, okay?

01:29:18.380 --> 01:29:20.910
You just relax, I’m gonna make
a phone call, all right?

01:29:22.610 --> 01:29:24.190
Rose. Rose, don’t go anywhere.

01:29:24.190 --> 01:29:25.650
Wait. Rose, please.

01:29:25.650 --> 01:29:27.650
Please don’t go anywhere, okay?
Just hang--

01:29:27.650 --> 01:29:29.990
Rose. Rose, wait! Rose!

01:29:56.050 --> 01:29:59.120
                   Joel.
       Rose, I saw a police APB
go out for you

01:29:59.120 --> 01:30:01.120
that says you’re dangerous.
What the fuck happened?

01:30:01.120 --> 01:30:02.390
I know what I need to do.
 What?

01:30:02.390 --> 01:30:05.460
This thing, it needs
all of its victims

01:30:05.460 --> 01:30:07.230
to pass it on
in order to survive,

01:30:07.230 --> 01:30:10.300
but if there’s no one else
around, it has no way to pass.

01:30:10.300 --> 01:30:11.790
As long as I’m alone,

01:30:11.790 --> 01:30:13.470
I can deprive it
of what it needs.

01:30:13.470 --> 01:30:15.170
That doesn’t make any sense.

01:30:15.170 --> 01:30:17.440
 Your plan is just to
avoid people forever?

01:30:17.440 --> 01:30:20.180
I am not gonna
keep running, okay?

01:30:20.930 --> 01:30:22.570
I’ve got to face it.

01:30:22.570 --> 01:30:24.910
Okay, Rose, I’m coming to you.
Just tell me where--

01:33:54.880 --> 01:33:56.390
Rose.

01:34:00.730 --> 01:34:02.090
Baby...

01:34:07.300 --> 01:34:09.440
Help me, please.

01:34:13.340 --> 01:34:15.740
Mommy made a mistake.

01:34:22.520 --> 01:34:24.210
Get the phone.

01:34:25.350 --> 01:34:27.180
Call for help.

01:34:37.370 --> 01:34:39.300
Rose!

01:38:51.080 --> 01:38:53.520
Rose.

01:38:58.990 --> 01:39:00.490
It’s okay, baby.

01:39:01.160 --> 01:39:02.490
Come here.

01:39:13.810 --> 01:39:17.400
I am so sorry.

01:39:19.880 --> 01:39:21.980
I-- I haven’t been a good mom.

01:39:25.180 --> 01:39:30.220
I want to be.
I really try to be.

01:39:30.220 --> 01:39:36.360
But sometimes
everything is just too much.

01:39:37.730 --> 01:39:41.230
There is something terrible
inside of me.

01:39:42.200 --> 01:39:45.770
I hate myself.
Stop. Stop. Stop.

01:39:46.400 --> 01:39:48.010
Are you ashamed of me?

01:39:49.300 --> 01:39:50.400
No.

01:39:51.140 --> 01:39:52.750
Then why did you let me die?

01:39:56.750 --> 01:39:59.150
 Why didn’t you save me?
It’s not my fault.

01:39:59.150 --> 01:40:01.950
You could have called for help.
              Stop. Stop it.

01:40:01.950 --> 01:40:03.990
 But you didn’t.
Stop it.

01:40:03.990 --> 01:40:06.890
You wished that I would die.
Because I was afraid of you!

01:40:06.890 --> 01:40:09.600
I was ten years old

01:40:10.800 --> 01:40:13.000
and you were a monster.

01:40:15.530 --> 01:40:20.530
And I know that it’s not fair.
You-- You needed help.

01:40:22.170 --> 01:40:23.610
But I couldn’t.

01:40:28.540 --> 01:40:30.620
And I have carried that guilt

01:40:31.850 --> 01:40:35.090
for my entire life.

01:40:38.490 --> 01:40:41.990
And I--
I have to let it go.

01:40:44.100 --> 01:40:45.870
I ha-- I have to let it go.

01:40:52.710 --> 01:40:54.340
This is not real.

01:40:55.140 --> 01:40:57.110
But Rose,

01:40:57.110 --> 01:41:01.280
your mind makes it real.

01:41:05.580 --> 01:41:06.920
What are you?

01:41:08.120 --> 01:41:10.120
Why are you
doing this to me?

01:41:10.920 --> 01:41:12.490
Because your mind...

01:41:13.420 --> 01:41:15.760
...is so inviting.

01:42:06.610 --> 01:42:10.480
You can’t escape
your mind, Rose.

01:42:17.760 --> 01:42:18.730
It’s--

01:42:20.030 --> 01:42:22.900
It’s my mind.

01:42:30.230 --> 01:42:32.040
You can’t escape it either.

01:42:47.520 --> 01:42:49.390
Rose!

01:42:52.160 --> 01:42:53.800
Rose!

01:44:17.280 --> 01:44:19.180
Holy shit.

01:44:21.740 --> 01:44:23.410
Are you okay?

01:44:23.410 --> 01:44:26.020
           Can I just
           come in for a sec?
Yeah. Yeah, yeah.

01:44:32.130 --> 01:44:33.590
Where have you
been?

01:44:38.100 --> 01:44:39.900
I’m sorry.

01:44:41.630 --> 01:44:47.340
I’m sorry for dragging you into
my whole fucked-up mess.

01:44:49.600 --> 01:44:51.440
For most of my life,

01:44:51.440 --> 01:44:57.650
I’ve been afraid of
letting people get too close,

01:44:58.650 --> 01:45:00.960
because I was afraid of...

01:45:03.990 --> 01:45:06.790
what they might see
if they really looked.

01:45:06.790 --> 01:45:11.860
And so I-- I put walls up,
and I kept people at a distance.

01:45:14.790 --> 01:45:16.070
And then...

01:45:19.500 --> 01:45:21.110
I met you,

01:45:21.110 --> 01:45:25.050
and I could feel
those walls coming down.

01:45:25.050 --> 01:45:28.080
And it scared the shit
out of me.

01:45:30.990 --> 01:45:32.450
And so...

01:45:33.620 --> 01:45:40.090
I was selfish,
and that was not fair to you.

01:45:41.720 --> 01:45:45.230
And I am so, so sorry.

01:45:46.690 --> 01:45:51.400
And I’m-- I’m being selfish
again by even asking,

01:45:51.400 --> 01:45:52.830
but do you think that--

01:45:52.830 --> 01:45:55.800
that I could stay here
and just...

01:45:58.080 --> 01:45:59.510
just sleep?

01:46:02.680 --> 01:46:04.020
Could you...

01:46:05.710 --> 01:46:08.450
stay with me while I sleep?

01:46:12.030 --> 01:46:13.000
Please.

01:46:14.720 --> 01:46:16.890
Yeah, of course
I’ll stay with you.

01:46:24.930 --> 01:46:26.900
I’ll stay with you forever.

01:46:33.350 --> 01:46:34.510
No.

01:46:41.550 --> 01:46:42.920
No.

01:46:43.990 --> 01:46:45.290
No, no, no, no.

01:46:46.260 --> 01:46:47.360
No, no.

01:47:02.110 --> 01:47:03.280
No.

01:47:27.700 --> 01:47:29.700
            Rose.

01:47:32.770 --> 01:47:35.370
No, no, no!

01:47:43.120 --> 01:47:45.120
Rose!
No.

01:47:45.120 --> 01:47:47.090
Rose, open the door!

01:47:48.980 --> 01:47:52.020
 Open the door.

01:47:53.490 --> 01:47:55.020
Rose!

01:48:05.000 --> 01:48:07.870
No!

01:48:08.640 --> 01:48:11.810
 No!
Fuck. Uh--

01:48:11.810 --> 01:48:13.480
Hold on. I’m coming!

01:48:13.480 --> 01:48:16.090
No!

01:48:19.390 --> 01:48:20.750
Rose!

01:48:23.290 --> 01:48:25.950
No!

01:49:07.400 --> 01:49:08.760
Rose.

01:49:43.030 --> 01:49:44.270
Rose?

01:49:50.540 --> 01:49:51.480
Rose?
